        "old_string": "bug_fixes:\n# *Changes expected to improve the state of the world and are unlikely to have negative effects*\n- area: outlier detection\n  change: |\n    Fixed :ref:`successful_active_health_check_uneject_host\n    <envoy_v3_api_field_config.cluster.v3.OutlierDetection.successful_active_health_check_uneject_host>`.",
        "new_string": "bug_fixes:\n# *Changes expected to improve the state of the world and are unlikely to have negative effects*\n- area: udp\n  change: |\n    Fixed a crash in the UDP proxy filter when a pre-existing cluster is updated via CDS (e.g., HostSet changes).\n    The filter was using ``std::unordered_map::emplace()`` which silently fails to update an existing entry,\n    leaving a stale reference to the old cluster. Changed to use ``insert_or_assign()`` to properly replace\n    the cluster info on updates.\n- area: outlier detection\n  change: |\n    Fixed :ref:`successful_active_health_check_uneject_host\n    <envoy_v3_api_field_config.cluster.v3.OutlierDetection.successful_active_health_check_uneject_host>`.",
